description:
"Lali Rupane, Eling Rasane"

Inspired by a quote on the back of the truck.
The two words we hide are Eling and Lali.
Eling is remembering and Lali is forgetting. Two contradicting words. We are encouraged to always be aware, remember, and be wary. Remember the God Who Has Life and never forget him. Eling rasane, considering that it feels like God's presence can only be felt, touched by the symptoms. Remembering the feelings and the heart is touching the essentials and forgetting the visible appearance is a necessity because the visible will change over time.
